    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to drive home in this fantastic and reliable vehicle! It's in good condition and has been well-cared for, making it the perfect companion for your daily drives and road trips alike. You'll love the smooth performance and well-maintained appearance of this dependable ride!",
      "price": 36500.0,
