    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and use. The engine and transmission are functional, but you can expect some minor oil leaks and a suspension that feels a bit loose on rougher roads. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, a few small dents, and some fading on the clear coat, while the interior shows significant wear on the driver's seat and some staining on the carpets. It has been maintained well enough to stay on the road, but a new owner should be prepared for some upcoming maintenance and cosmetic repairs to bring it back to its best.",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
