    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen of automotive excellence, this vehicle is offered in pristine, showroom-quality condition. Meticulously maintained and preserved with the utmost care, it retains its original luster and mechanical precision. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the immaculate interior appointments, reflects a standard of ownership that is truly rare. This is an acquisition opportunity for the discerning buyer who demands a vehicle indistinguishable from new.",
      "price": 48500.0,
